.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: black, azure, coral, lilac, mauve
There are 5 different nationalities: pakistani, chinese, italian, australian, french
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-fanta, 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, cola
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: blackmaster, alhambra, chaman, baccarat, game
5 different pets are kept: goldfrog, pony, hamster, frog, rabbit
1. the pakistani is the person who likes coral
2. the swedish is the owner of the hamster
3. the chinese is the person drinking hot-chocolate
4. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes lilac
5. the person who likes azure is the person drinking 7up
6. the chaman-smoker is the owner of the pony
7. the person who likes mauve is the alhambra-smoker
8. the person drinking fanta is in the middle
9. the australian is on the far left
10. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfrog
11. the owner of the rabbits is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker
12. the blackmaster-smoker is the person drinking soy-fanta
13. the italian is the baccarat-smoker
14. the australian is on the left or right of the person who likes black
15. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking cola

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    mauve	|     black	|      coral	|     azure	|     lilac	|
| Nationality	|   australian	|    chinese	|    pakistani	|    italian	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     goldfrog	|    rabbit	|     pony	|     frog	|      hamster	|
| Beverage	|    cola	|     hot-chocolate	|     fanta	|    7up	|      soy-fanta	|
| Cigar		|   alhambra	|    game	|  chaman	|    baccarat	|   blackmaster	|
